#: src/slic3r/GUI/ConfigManipulation.cpp:81
#, c-format
msgid ""
"The Spiral Vase mode requires:\n"
"- one perimeter\n"
"- no top solid layers\n"
"- 0% fill density\n"
"- no support material\n"
"- Ensure vertical shell thickness enabled\n"
"- Detect thin walls disabled"
msgstr ""
"螺旋花瓶模式要求:\n"
"- 一個周界\n"
"- 無頂部實心層\n"
"- 0% 填滿密度\n"
"- 無支撐材料\n"
"- 確保啟用垂直外殼厚度\n"
"- 偵測關閉的薄壁"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/ConfigManipulation.cpp:89
msgid "Shall I adjust those settings in order to enable Spiral Vase?"
msgstr "我應調整這些設置以啟用螺旋花瓶嗎?"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/ConfigManipulation.cpp:90
msgid "Spiral Vase"
msgstr "螺旋花瓶"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/ConfigManipulation.cpp:115
msgid ""
"The Wipe Tower currently supports the non-soluble supports only\n"
"if they are printed with the current extruder without triggering a tool "
"change.\n"
"(both support_material_extruder and support_material_interface_extruder need "
"to be set to 0)."
msgstr ""
"清除塔目前僅支援非可溶性支架\n"
"如果它們與當前擠出機一起列印,而不觸發刀具更換。\n"
"(support_material_extruder 和 support_material_interface_extruder 都需要設置"
"為 0)。"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/ConfigManipulation.cpp:119
msgid "Shall I adjust those settings in order to enable the Wipe Tower?"
msgstr "我應調整這些設置以啟用擦拭塔嗎?"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/ConfigManipulation.cpp:120
#: src/slic3r/GUI/ConfigManipulation.cpp:140
msgid "Wipe Tower"
msgstr "擦料塔"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/ConfigManipulation.cpp:136
msgid ""
"For the Wipe Tower to work with the soluble supports, the support layers\n"
"need to be synchronized with the object layers."
msgstr ""
"為了擦拭塔與可溶性支架配合使用,支撐層\n"
"需要與物件圖層同步。"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/ConfigManipulation.cpp:139
msgid "Shall I synchronize support layers in order to enable the Wipe Tower?"
msgstr "我應同步支撐層以啟用擦除塔嗎?"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/ConfigManipulation.cpp:159
